{"about_the_game":"Johnny Chainsaw is a single player puzzle platformer where players don\u2019t have a jump button. Immerse yourself in this world of power structures, ethical dilemmas, and struggles in responding to change.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">No Jump Button</h2>Use the world to navigate obstacles and levels. How can you use the world to cross this gap without a jump button?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/711840/extras/gifStore-2.gif?t=1680040927\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Two Modes<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story mode: A discovery at the center of the planet, a response hampered by power struggles, and the inevitable change that threatens the world. You decide what happens to the inhabitants of Corut and how their lives will be forever changed.<br></li><li>Standard mode: Complete the game without story mode elements. Perfect for streaming, speedrunning, or enjoying weird platforming mechanics without narrative screens interrupting game flow.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>40 short levels<br></li><li>6 boss fights<br></li><li>Death counter and timer<br></li><li>Collectables<br></li><li>Character Sheets<br></li><li>Rich story and Custscenes (story mode only)<br></li><li>Quick resets after character death - get right back in the action<br></li><li>Achievements</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Decide the Fate of the World (Story Mode Only)</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/711840/extras/oscarTalking.gif?t=1680040927\" /><br>When Yarbor's lead researcher Ivan discovers a change at the planet's core, a power struggle ensues at the company. This conflict forever changes the lives of all mechanics and organics on Corut. <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Reveal Ivan's discovery<br></li><li>Explore the power struggle and its ramifications<br></li><li>Recognize your part in the this conflict<b